message.entry: N-D sparse output arrays are not supported.
Sparse integer array arithmetic operations are not supported.
Sparse single array arithmetic operations are not supported.
Specified function handle produces invalid output dimensions. The function handle must be a binary elementwise function.
Output class is not consistent.
Output has to be consistently full or consistently sparse.
Output is not numeric.
Output cannot be sparse when inputs are full.
Operands must be real for &,|,xor.
Complex integer arithmetic is not supported.
Integer arguments not supported for ATAN2.
Integer arguments not supported for ATAN2D.
Integer arguments not supported for HYPOT.
Operands must be numeric arrays.
Undefined function ''{0}'' for input arguments of type ''{1}''.
First Argument must be a function handle.
Non-singleton dimensions of the two input arrays must match each other.
Mixed integer class inputs are not supported.
Classes of operands are not supported.
Unknown operator.
